name: Rø YAąstáy
description:
/Use the fruits that the earth gives you with respect and only out of necessity. 
Ask permission and offer Yastay her favorite food. 
Keep your pact, and never reveal it, because it will unleash his fury with his devilish head. 
Spirit, man and animal, of indescribable beauty, his divine mission is to protect the herds from the overflows of human ambition./

Photographed sculpture made up of polymer clay, waste material, and natural elements (earth, seeds, and twigs)
